item.title: Economy Reset not working!
item.dc:creator: @Fridder Fridder
item.description:
@Fridder wrote:

Wrong section. Try Server help instead.

You have to go into the folder that has the EconomyReset.java file, then make a new .bat called ‘EcoReset.bat’, and inside of it put this:

@echo off
java EconomyReset
pause

And that’s it.
